usdLogAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the logging managment component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdLogAgentV1.name: usdLogAgentV1
usdLogAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the logging managment component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the Log component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 1.3 system release.
usdLogAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the logging managment application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the single syslog destination was replaced with a table of syslog destinations and the syslog facility was added.

usdLogAgentV2.name: usdLogAgentV2
usdLogAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the logging managment component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the Log component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdLogAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the logging managment application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
